OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers being balloted
OL,4,Cfor strike action
OL,6,FAround 400 Birmingham refuse workers
OL,7,Fare being balloted for strike action
OL,8,Fover claims that a council is removing
OL,9,Fa critical safety role.
OL,11,FUnite the union has sighted the death
OL,12,Fof Coventry bin man David Carpenter,
OL,13,Fwho was crushed in a lorry compactor
OL,14,Fin January 2023, as a reason why the
OL,15,Frole is essential and must be kept.
OL,17,FThe vote comes after Unite the union
OL,18,Fclaims the council refused to back
OL,19,Fdown on its plans to cut pay by
OL,20,Fremoving the safety critical Waste
OL,21,FRecycling and Collection Officer role.
