OL,3,CBirmingham bin workers being balloted
OL,4,Cfor strike action
OL,6,FThe ballot for strike action opens on
OL,7,FFriday, 22 November and closes on
OL,8,FWednesday, 4 December.
OL,10,FBirmingham City Council says it is
OL,11,Fcommitted to working with its
OL,12,Fcolleagues across the service for the
OL,13,Fbest outcome so that "we deliver a
OL,14,Fconsistent and reliable service that
OL,15,FBirmingham residents deserve".
OL,17,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,18,Fsaid: "Birmingham council's plans to
OL,19,Fremove a safety critical role to
OL,20,Fattack workers' pay are abhorrent.
