OL,6,F"Birmingham's refuse workers go above
OL,7,Fand beyond and are already shouldering
OL,8,Funfair demands for a crisis they
OL,9,Fdidn't create and shouldn't have to
OL,10,Fpay for. They have Unite's total
OL,11,Fbacking."
OL,13,FMost of the around 150 staff
OL,14,Fperforming the WRCO role have been
OL,15,Fworking for Birmingham waste
OL,16,Fcollection services for more than 30
OL,17,Fyears.
