OL,6,FCllr Majid Mahmood, cabinet member for
OL,7,Fenvironment and transport, said: "The
OL,8,Fconsultation period with our
OL,9,Frecognised unions has come to an end
OL,10,Fand a decision has been taken to
OL,11,Fproceed with the proposal to change to
OL,12,Fthe new operating arrangements.
OL,14,F"Ensuring the safety of our employees
OL,15,Fand residents is taken extremely
OL,16,Fseriously, and health and safety is
OL,17,Feveryone's responsibility.
