OL,6,F"We are now undertaking the post
OL,7,Fconsultation steps to ensure all
OL,8,FBirmingham City Council colleagues
OL,9,Faffected by the change in working
OL,10,Farrangements are supported.
OL,12,F"There are several options that are
OL,13,Favailable to suit different personal
OL,14,Fcircumstances, these include opting
OL,15,Ffor voluntary redundancy, promotion or
OL,16,Fredeployment.
OL,18,F"We recognise that this is an
OL,19,Funsettling time, and we have moved
OL,20,Fquickly, to minimise this period of
OL,21,Funcertainty for everyone.
